WEBVTT

00:08:27.342 --> 00:08:30.272
What is in your head and your mind

00:08:30.296 --> 00:08:32.222
and what you have seen and witnessed ...

00:08:32.246 --> 00:08:37.629
One of the things that it's good
to remember, always,

00:08:37.653 --> 00:08:40.432
is that when you opened that restaurant,

00:08:40.456 --> 00:08:44.638
whites and blacks could not
eat together in this city.

00:08:45.041 --> 00:08:46.664
It was against the law.

00:08:46.688 --> 00:08:50.839
And yet they did, at Dooky Chase.
Tell me about that.

00:08:50.863 --> 00:08:52.277
LC: They did, there.

00:08:52.301 --> 00:08:54.336
Well, my mother-in-law first started this,

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:56.205
and the reason she started is,

00:08:56.229 --> 00:09:03.226
because her husband was sickly,
and he would go out --